1 It changes all input to lower case
2 It splits input1 into multiple words
3 It loops through the array to check and see if input1 is equal to input2
4 It adds +1 to a word check counter if input1 is equal to input2
5 It outputs word check counter

  Input            || Output
1 "Simon is named  || "simon is named simon"
   Simon"          ||
2 "Simon is named  || "simon" "is" "named" "simon"
   Simon"          || 
3  input1, input2  || loop through and check if item in input1 is equal to input2
4  input1, input2  || if equal, +1 to counter variable
5  input1, input2  || counter variable to be displayed to user
